## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- We will execute a standalone TypeScript script validating the **Sequential Processing** pipeline.
- We will verify token rejection thresholds, schema validation, and content completeness gates using mocked texts.

### Manual Verification
1. Attempt to send out-of-range text (e.g., larger than context window) to trigger token limit fallback.
2. Send natural requests like "Log 45m on NJS-123 diagnosing DB issues".
3. Verify that the orchestrator rejects bad payloads, calls the model securely, and completes the transaction using the Circuit Breaker logic.
